      "message": "I would add mehthod 'contains' to publishedFileCache, and than rewrite this logic a bit, like in this (pseudo) code.\n\nconsider following logic:\n\n        Path localFilePath = fileData.fileData.getLocalFilePath();\n        boolean shouldBePublished = !cache.contains(localFilePath);\n        if (shouldBePublished) {\n            try {\n                shouldBePublished = checkIfFileWasNotPublishedYet();\n            } catch (DatafileTaskException e) {\n                log();\n            }\n        } \n        if(!shouldBePublished) log();\n        return shouldBePublished;",
