      "message": "1. Done\n2. First if can change the value of shouldBePublished so the second can't be else case.\nThe logic here works like that:\n (publishedFilesCache.put(localFilePath) == null) - checks if file was put into cache\n- if it is in cache, then dmaap check is skipped and file is not published\n- it it is not in cache, dmaap check determines if the file should be published",
